反映」，她促請該處使用酌情權讓持雙程證的母親可獲得香港身份證。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:30:51.000Z","msg":"社協幹禍港一定要來香港讀大陸沒學校?"},{"pid":"2f1f22291c7dc6a358f9d3fdc8a9d6d761b93ef6","tid":765854,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:34:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daf5a506036271a50797dd903f877c7aaba4afd8","tid":765854,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"又係女人社工"},{"pid":"60b9bb8c1765d4d18f3ac784c5be7b2475cca522","tid":765854,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾機構真係影撚衰哂社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n施麗珊你幾時死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <